OL,3,CSpice Girl-turned-student Mel B to
OL,4,Creceive honorary doctorate
OL,6,FSinger Mel B is to receive an honorary
OL,7,Fdoctorate in recognition of her work
OL,8,Fto campaign for domestic violence
OL,9,Fvictims.
OL,11,FThe former Spice Girls member, whose
OL,12,Ffull name is Melanie Brown, will be
OL,13,Fgiven the award by Leeds Beckett
OL,14,FUniversity for her services to her
OL,15,Fhome city.
OL,17,FIt comes after she enrolled on a
OL,18,Fcourse in trauma-informed care at the
OL,19,Funiversity.
