OL,6,FThe 49-year-old said the award had
OL,7,Fbeen "life changing".
OL,9,F"I didn't just want to accept an
OL,10,Faward," she said.
OL,12,F"I wanted to be accepted as a student
OL,13,Fat Leeds Beckett. Not only have I been
OL,14,Fawarded this degree, but I was also
OL,15,Faccepted as a student on the trauma-
OL,16,Finformed care course, which has been a
OL,17,Fhuge step for me in so many ways.
