OL,3,CSpice Girl-turned-student Mel B to
OL,4,Creceive honorary doctorate
OL,6,FProf Peter Slee, Leeds Beckett
OL,7,FUniversity's vice chancellor, said:
OL,8,F"As a child of this city who reached
OL,9,Fthe top of her industry and then used
OL,10,Fher platform to advocate for those who
OL,11,Fshared her hardships, Melanie is
OL,12,Fexactly the type of citizen we are
OL,13,Fhere to champion."
OL,15,FBrown will receive her honorary
OL,16,Fdoctorate during graduation week this
OL,17,Fmonth.
